---
// src/components/CompetitiveAdvantage.astro
---
<section class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 py-20 lg:py-24">
  <div class="gap-8 items-center py-8 px-4 mx-auto max-w-screen-xl xl:gap-16 md:grid md:grid-cols-2 sm:py-16 lg:px-6">
    <img class="w-full dark:hidden rounded-lg shadow-xl" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1552664730-d307ca884978?w=800" alt="Competitive Advantage Illustration">
    <img class="w-full hidden dark:block rounded-lg shadow-xl" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1552664730-d307ca884978?w=800" alt="Competitive Advantage Illustration">
    <div class="mt-4 md:mt-0">
      <h2 class="mb-4 text-3xl lg:text-4xl tracking-tight font-extrabold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
        Keunggulan Kompetitif Kami
      </h2>
      <p class="mb-6 font-light text-gray-500 md:text-lg dark:text-gray-400">
        Kami tidak hanya menyediakan teknologi, tetapi juga kemitraan strategis untuk kesuksesan jangka panjang Anda.
      </p>
      <ul class="space-y-4">
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-500" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg>
          </div>
          <div class="ml-3">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold dark:text-white">Solusi Terkustomisasi</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">Kami merancang solusi AI yang sesuai dengan kebutuhan unik bisnis Anda.</p>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-500" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg>
          </div>
          <div class="ml-3">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold dark:text-white">Dukungan Ahli</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">Tim ahli kami siap membantu Anda di setiap langkah implementasi dan optimisasi.</p>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-500" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg>
          </div>
          <div class="ml-3">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold dark:text-white">ROI Terukur</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">Kami fokus pada memberikan hasil yang terukur dan keuntungan investasi yang jelas.</p>
          </div>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
